realtimeweb.stickyweb.converters
Class JsonConverter

Object
  realtimeweb.stickyweb.converters.JsonConverter

public class JsonConverter
extends Object

An internal class that provides a convenient converter for JSON formatted data. This class will convert JSON maps to HashMaps and JSON lists to ArrayLists.
